
This document describes the steps necessary to integrate the
Tax.pm module into the opensrs-sf code.
This was developed with version 2.14

This is not a complete set of instructions.
It is meant for developers.

The file Tax.pm is placed in lib/Payment

The file patch1 shows an example of how to modify the templates
to display the tax name variables. This particular patch is for
soe of the domain/renew templates.

The file patch2 shows how to modify the cgi programs to make use
of the new module. This particular patch is for the renew.cgi program.

taxtable.conf should be placed in the etc directory.
Add the following to local.conf to include it.
<<include taxtable.conf>>
